      • countContainsPrimaryDimensionValButNotAsLast

        public int countContainsPrimaryDimensionValButNotAsLast(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Integer> givenPrimaryDimensionVal)
        Count num of non-last activity objects with the at least one matching primary dimension val of the given.

        e.g., if primary dimension is activity id, then it works similar to countContainsActivityNameButNotAsLast(), i.e., count the number of non-last aos which have activity ids same as given primaryDimensionVal. Primary dimension is an array list because in case of merger an activity object can have multiple values for a dimension.

        Parameters:
        activityNameToCheck -
        Returns:
        num of non-last activity objects with the at least one matching primary dimension val of the given
